						<summary>

						<p>This gives a list of the lands, 3 <hi rend="italic">vēli</hi> in all, which had been endowed to the temple of Mahādēva by several persons, and which were now exempted from taxes by order of the king <hi rend="italic">(Uḍaiyār).</hi> The writing seems to be of the time of <hi rend="bold">Rājēndra-Chōḷa I.</hi> </p>						

						</summary>
